<dec f='include/unicode/curramt.h' l='51' type='void icu_66::CurrencyAmount::CurrencyAmount(const icu_66::Formattable &amp; amount, icu_66::ConstChar16Ptr isoCode, UErrorCode &amp; ec)'/>
<doc f='include/unicode/curramt.h' l='41'>/**
     * Construct an object with the given numeric amount and the given
     * ISO currency code.
     * @param amount a numeric object; amount.isNumeric() must be TRUE
     * @param isoCode the 3-letter ISO 4217 currency code; must not be
     * NULL and must have length 3
     * @param ec input-output error code. If the amount or the isoCode
     * is invalid, then this will be set to a failing value.
     * @stable ICU 3.0
     */</doc>
